{"tid":1633062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港人，點解唔可以唔罷工」?","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:31:22.000Z","uid":12929,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a11d5598a6b6acc7d764dc4edf9ceaf3e6fffbaa","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"If we burn, you burn with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔係整係同政權講，而係同時同所有沉默的大多數講。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 (和勇，中立) 唔團結就會一齊輸</span></span>，唔好諗住講兩句好慘，願早日康復呢d 令自己好過嘅嘢有可以贏。連月黎香港人成長咗好多，但制度暴力、警暴、濫暴卻與日俱增<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。民記曾經講過「當解放軍入城，我地會番屋企訓教。」。點解面對手足無差別地被香港共安襲擊、拘捕我地唔可以罷工抵抗？<br />\n<br />\n多一個好多，講咗好耐，聽咗好耐。10.6 港九大遊行好多人，正正因為呢句。而罷工行動（3日以上）係同樣道理，當每一位被罷工者成為一位罷工者，咁就會出然一個vicious cycle,好似喪屍片咁，before you know it, 全城都會罷緊工。<br />\n<br />\n和你飛、和你塞點解政府驚到要去法庭申請禁制令？正正因為香港嘅economic output 就係春袋，我地要團結大大力錫落佢先會有希望。<br />\n<br />\n1999唔識講嘢，不過希望大家有準備「被罷工」嘅心態。罷工期行動以口罩為記。全港大罷工在即，香港人買定糧食儲備。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔係得個講。<span style=\"color: gold;\">「是你教我們和平示威是沒有用的」</span>）"},{"pid":"8c70be3a4e30216da7e3f9dce7a00941ac48086b","tid":1633062,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"經過8月5就知香港人無可能罷工<br />\n<br />\n而家已經做到近乎罷工效果"},{"pid":"db46c390d89dd54965cc3af35d4294f579a3dfa2","tid":1633062,"uid":207553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"既然連仔唔整英文台,我地就自制英文台<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ejrhgT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ejrhgT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"74c7b9953501bbceac19b6e77ca4b2e0b30886f2","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"13077445404e9b0c98f48759775969f164717aeb","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c70be3a4e30216da7e3f9dce7a00941ac48086b","tid":1633062,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"經過8月5就知香港人無可能罷工<br />\n<br />\n而家已經做到近乎罷工效果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"6.9之前我地都唔知原來會有100萬人上街<br />\n<br />\n近乎罷工只限星期六日，星期一至五黨鐵就會核爆都會繼續運作。對香港係冇影響㗎"},{"pid":"079cfc2d925c041c23ed176c52504e78c43a3b69","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"af9affc2d77754927c73cec8450e625de1dfcd3e","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:16.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"b2d50e7a42700e814da7ae8d0e0f69c0814f7579","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"0b921e750d8b78a58df83b57c0cb77aba5723598","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:40.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"ffe24e8f40e60f4740c635156b7172894dbdc48c","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"推 6/10"},{"pid":"61a57c95c852ab7680d42fe681a946a621eed875","tid":1633062,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"推 7/10"},{"pid":"0cac96a875b739d86c31f6e58ac47743f642c2b3","tid":1633062,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https